News Releases, Media Advisories

March 10, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
THE BROTHERHOOD OF LOCOMOTIVE ENGINEERS PAC FUND
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on the Brotherhood of Locomotive Engineers PAC Fund. This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: FEC Releases Final Audit Report on the Brotherhood of Locomotive Engineers PAC Fund
